location.fullValue: Thrive Monterrey Plan, The Enclave At Kamden's Cove

data.description: Cutest house on the block! This home is in a great location and move in ready. Just minutes from I-65 and many retail shops, this 3 bedroom, two bath home is perfect for an individual or family. The kitchen and bathrooms have granite countertops. There is LVP throughout the living space with carpet in the bedrooms and tile in the baths. There is a spacious two car garage and two attic accesses for additional storage.  The large back yard backs up to a wooded area which is perfect for outdoor fun. Call to see it today!
